text: Ng Shu Wai (born 27 May 1985) is a Malaysian gymnast. He competed in seven events at the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Malaysian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Malaysia Category:Gymnasts at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:People from Perak Category:Commonwealth Games medallists in gymnastics Category:Commonwealth Games silver medallists for Malaysia
